 target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1</a><br />\n［學術］中咗催淚彈同胡椒噴霧解決方法 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223200/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223200/page/1</a><br />\n[廣傳][長文]長期革命，每個人都要準備對抗催淚彈/胡椒噴磅必須用品 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">裝備</span></span><br />\n&lt;抗爭手冊&gt; <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1085603/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1085603/page/2</a><br />\n振興香港消費！全城戶外運動裝備及須知 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1224572/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1224572/page/1</a><br />\n知己知彼 百戰百勝圖解香港警察裝備 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1206461/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1206461/page/1</a><br />\n最近有個新喪屍GAME IDEA <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1222684/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1222684/page/1</a><br />\n[突發] 621 雙方陣營裝備分析 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240449/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240449/page/1</a><br />\n[魔防的重要性］所有人都要有足夠魔防 N95同泳鏡係最低要求 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242265/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242265/page/1</a><br />\n星期五嘅野餐行動 請現在立即做兩樣野 購買裝備 同 加強文宣 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241812/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241812/page/1</a><br />\n[突發]新假期繼野餐之後又癡咗線 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242741/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242741/page/1</a><br />\n緊急！邊度可以買魔防裝 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242751/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242751/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">盾牌</span></span><br />\n[歷史台][積極備盾] 盾牌陣不是亂擺一通的 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241049/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241049/page/1</a><br />\n廉價盾牌材料 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1200677/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1200677/page/1</a><br />\n對付警犬最強盾牌buff <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216654/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216654/page/1</a><br />\n得黑警有盾牌？我都有！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1225742/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1225742/page/1</a><br />\n盾牌警棍頭盔：反政府示威者裝備不輸警察 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240310/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240310/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">物資</span></span><br />\n作為一個物資站站長，我想同大家道個歉 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1222678/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1222678/page/1</a><br />\n野餐物資／通訊檢討小組（重開）<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217849/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217849/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">鐵馬</span></span><br />\n鐵馬一定要放最前！鐵馬一定要有流動性！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1238720/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1238720/page/1</a><br />\n[人人都要識] 倒三角扎鐵馬 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240447/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240447/page/1</a><br />\n鐵馬最新安置法 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216269/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216269/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">地形</span></span><br />\n圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">IT</span></span><br />\n[正式上架] 手機抗警犬 用相機Scan數字即出黑警資料 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241300/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"808ea079bf44d963181634ed05b7cd2c2781640f","tid":1243324,"uid":190928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82fac8ea7f1509a3d14f03aacf145254f9871345","tid":1243324,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab368aac04b9a016a71a0996cda3be113f4236a","tid":1243324,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:50:40.000Z","msg":"[香港加油] 想喺聽日deadline前激勵下大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243430</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5fbf13eb0f82bbbb3645a7647ff4bd601f6e4f54","tid":1243324,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6d4167e3384651ea3ad837009f7210e74ba5f81","tid":1243324,"uid":120070,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:35:50.000Z","msg":"唔好發夢 民陣？ 呸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:50:43.000Z","msg":"心水清"},{"pid":"727bb36b1165041bfbc1f7078d62efcb5a3353e1","tid":1243324,"uid":257737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:50:51.000Z","msg":"講支持和平啦"},{"pid":"91d8564a1153ba709443ac94703dbebcc7d60489","tid":1243324,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:51:32.000Z","msg":"聽記招講左支持"},{"pid":"cb930c9be5c09d14ef1d197f0ba54bbc33bc25da","tid":1243324,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"唔得，因為各個組織都各懷鬼胎"},{"pid":"3f9efc90159a7ca3dab5098cfe5260cee0c800f1","tid":1243324,"uid":7662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"